== Substitution \[/\] ==

The expression \[A/x] φ means that every time we see the variable x in the formula φ we replace it with A.

=== Examples ===

* \[B/x\] [edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/sbc-oddSuccessor | (C ∙ x = A) ↔ C ∙ B = A	]

* \[A/y\] [edit/peano/peano_thms.gh/sbc-addcom | (y + B = B + y) ↔ A + B = B + A ]

